      <div class="exp-header">
        <span class="exp-verdict" id="verdict-104"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="exp-body">
        DHCP (Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol) dynamically assigns IP addresses to end and intermediary devices. This service automates the process of configuring devices on IP networks, allowing them to use network services such as DNS, NTP, and any communication protocol based on UDP or TCP.
